    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>\n                  The immune responses underlying the infection of severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) remain unclear. To help understand the pathology of coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19) pandemics, public data were analyzed and the expression of\n                  <jats:italic>PDCD1</jats:italic>\n                  (encoding PD-1) and\n                  <jats:italic>CD274</jats:italic>\n                  (encoding PD-L1) in T cells and macrophages were identified to correlate positively with COVID-19 severity.\n                </jats:p>",
